      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative automotive specimen, currently offered in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning collector, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that maintains its original factory integrity. Beyond its aesthetic perfection, the mechanical systems have been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, mirroring its original delivery specifications. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising caliber and documented excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
