      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of uncompromising caliber. This motorcar remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting meticulous stewardship and an exhaustive maintenance history. Every aesthetic and mechanical detail has been preserved to an exacting standard, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. An exceptional opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking an investment-grade specimen.",
      "price": 46850.0,
