      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's in absolutely pristine, mint condition! It's been pampered since day one and honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
