    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a concours-level example of the 996.2 wide-body silhouette. At its heart is the 3.6L flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus timing and lift, delivering seamless power through a 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle. This specimen has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent bore-scope inspection confirming pristine cylinder walls. The chassis retains its factory-tuned suspension and viscous-clutch all-wheel-drive system, providing exceptional lateral grip. Finished in flawless paint with an undercarriage still showing factory cosmoline, the vehicle features Turbo-spec Brembo monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors with zero thermal fatigue. A mechanically perfect, turn-key investment for the purist.",
